Package poisedPackage

Class NewPerson

java.lang.Object
poisedPackage.NewPerson
public class NewPerson
extends java.lang.Object
Project Management System for Poised. NewPerson is a child class/ subclass that creates and displays a person object.

It has attributes for variables for this class 'NewPerson' It has an constructor to create objects for the person. It has an method to display the created person. The MainMenu class calls on methods from this class to add new projects to 'completedProject.txt'.

    • NewPerson

      public NewPerson​(java.lang.String personType, java.lang.String name, int number, java.lang.String email, java.lang.String address)
      Project Management System for Poised. NewPerson constructor has 5 parameters which information needs to be passed in to create a new person as an object.

      A NewPerson object will consist of (personType,name,number,email and address).

      Parameters:
      personType - personType (e.g. customer, contractor or architect )
      name - name full name.
      number - contact number.
      email - email address.
      address - physical address.
